{"id": "1371889876147900446", "channel_id": "1371889876147900446", "type": 0, "author_id": "452731110556696596", "author_name": "aurora3981", "author_bot": false, "content": "After playing the card once, Master of Understanding is no longer applied.\nThe card on the left, I have not been played before thus shows strike 0 cost.\nThe card I'm hold have been played before thus bugged strike 1 cost.\n\nAlso the translation doesn't match, Master of Omniscient Verity should be Master of Understanding.", "timestamp": "2025-05-13T16:40:34.955000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1371889876378849400", "filename": "Screenshot_20250514_003314_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 308368, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1371889876147900446/1371889876378849400/Screenshot_20250514_003314_Morimens.jpg?ex=69cbf903&is=69caa783&hm=2688121d0bca4752bd45c17507eff58fde700e2e2a3b0387e04058ce7ca11786&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1371889876147900446", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Tawil Master of Understanding Not Working", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1371786919796670526", "channel_id": "1371786919796670526", "type": 0, "author_id": "371597034865819652", "author_name": "ahugebattleship", "author_bot": false, "content": "Horla's 'Fear' emotion does not increase the power gained by Tawil's Timestrung Pinion. Here it gives 10 power both normally and when Fear is active.\n\nFear does increase the power gained by Clementine's Quasar (Leap) effects and from Hamelin's strike, defense and Memory Rondo so it appears to be a bug specific to Tawil.\n\n___\n\n霍拉的“恐惧”情绪不会提升塔维尔的“时弦之翼”所获得的力量。此处，它在正常情况下和恐惧激活时都会提供10点力量。\n\n恐惧确实会提升克莱门汀的“类星体（跳跃）”效果以及哈梅林的攻击、防御和“记忆回旋曲”所获得的力量，因此这似乎是塔维尔特有的一个漏洞。", "timestamp": "2025-05-13T09:51:28.248000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😲", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1371786920304312370", "filename": "32969839.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 3543678, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1371786919796670526/1371786920304312370/32969839.jpg?ex=69cc41e0&is=69caf060&hm=016bced7a3c1ba8ab4dbaf254bfb9e6ae4eb825bb79de9db90e07a4af501c6fb&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1371786919796670526", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Horla's Fear emotion does not increase Tawil's power gained from Timestrung Pinion", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1371789290861760523", "channel_id": "1371786919796670526", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@&1166257943742787615>", "timestamp": "2025-05-13T10:00:53.554000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1371786919796670526", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Horla's Fear emotion does not increase Tawil's power gained from Timestrung Pinion", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1371789517878460416", "channel_id": "1371786919796670526", "type": 0, "author_id": "371597034865819652", "author_name": "ahugebattleship", "author_bot": false, "content": "From more testing, this may just be a text display error on the card. When I actually use Timestrung Pinion normally it gives 11 power instead of the 10 it says on the card. When I use Timestrung Pinion with the Fear emotion active it gives 14 power instead of the 10 it says.\n\n---\n\n经过更多测试，这可能只是卡牌上的文字显示错误。我正常使用时弦之翼时，它给出的力量是 11，而不是卡牌上显示的 10。当我在恐惧表情下使用时弦之翼时，它给出的力量是 14，而不是卡牌上显示的 10。", "timestamp": "2025-05-13T10:01:47.679000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1371786919796670526", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Horla's Fear emotion does not increase Tawil's power gained from Timestrung Pinion", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
